### 4.3 Cross-check vs system.access.column_lineage  ← Summary line: parsed=N, runtime=N, mismatches=N (DETAILS in .lineage.md)

---

## 5. Common usage / JOINs                           ← How analysts actually query this object

### 5.1 Sample queries                               ← 1–2 real SQL snippets from query_history or skills/_de_existing
### 5.2 Common JOIN partners                         ← Table: JOIN to | Condition | Purpose
### 5.3 Gotchas                                      ← Bullet list of traps (passthrough sentinels, schema drift, NULL semantics)

---

